Subject: [PATCH 2/9 v9] V4L: add two new ioctl()s for multi-size videobuffer
 management
In-Reply-To: <Pine.LNX.4.64.1109271847310.7004@axis700.grange>
Message-ID: <Pine.LNX.4.64.1109281502380.30317@axis700.grange>
